title: The FoodSaver® FM1510 Fresh Food Preservation System -  Overview
description: The FoodSaver Fresh Food Preservation System seals in freshness of foods stored in the fridge, pantry and on the go. Easily and conveniently vacuum seal FoodSaver Fresh Containers and Vacuum Zipper Bags for storage of everyday foods, leftovers and prep-ahead ingredients. Its compact design is made for everyday countertop use and its one-touch sealing allows for hand-free operation once the sealing process starts.

transcripts: Air is the enemy of food freshness. Over twenty percent of fruits, vegetables, and grains are wasted in the US that's over five hundred dollars a year worth of produce and ingredients, waste no more. Vacuum sealing is the best solution to keep your food fresh longer with the new FoodSaver fresh food preservation system it's never been this simple. Now you can keep food fresh up to two times longer it's designed to work exclusively with the FoodSaver fresh containers and zipper bags just press start and it does the rest. The vacuum process stops automatically when freshness is sealed in. Perfect for storing your favorite foods in the fridge or the pantry or to take on the go. Trust your food freshness to the new FoodSaver fresh food preservation system.
